"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-05-17-Olympic-champion-Horigome-falls-in-Olympic-Qualifier-Series-1tFOZzb0q4g-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  Tokyo Olympic skateboarding champion Yuto Horigome of Japan was the big name to fall on day one of the ground-breaking Olympic Qualifier Series on Thursday, scoring 81.88 points to finish 17th, just one spot below the bar to qualify for the semi-final round.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuto_Horigome_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.9999999629922065, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yuto Horigome\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuto_Horigome_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuto_Horigome_(skateboarder)\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9372363511923101, \"rank\": 0.06667704043278602, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not satisfied with my performance today, but I still have a chance to secure a position in [the] Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will work harder and try to be among Paris Olympic skateboarders,\\\" said the 25-year-old, while fellow Japanese Netsuke Kairi posted a triumphant 90.41 to qualify first.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999828628462, \"rank\": 1.71369860865176e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9895044890854058, \"rank\": 0.010568104643337092, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netsuke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Netsuke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netsuke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netsuke\"}, {\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Kingdom_Hearts\", \"score\": 0.9926290513105873, \"rank\": 0.007425679931420397, \"text\": \"Kairi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Kingdom_Hearts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Kingdom_Hearts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Horigome was not alone in facing an early exit.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tokyo Olympic silver medalist Kelvin Hoefler of Brazil also failed to advance after only posting a best score of 68.44.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999998990461, \"rank\": 6.418120209038052e-11, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin_Hoefler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelvin Hoefler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin_Hoefler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin_Hoefler\"}, {\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9328273459048955, \"rank\": 0.07195710626960822, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the men's sport climbing competition, reigning Olympic champion Alberto Gines Lopez from Spain finished third out of 46 athletes in the bouldering qualification.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberto_Giacometti\", \"score\": 0.9999999953461156, \"rank\": 4.554043594110796e-09, \"text\": \"Alberto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberto_Giacometti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberto_Giacometti\"}, {\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.7296681414600722, \"rank\": 0.3504737183975387, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\"}, {\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9958844653974637, \"rank\": 0.004123016934281716, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Korea's Lee Dohyun took first place with 84.9 points.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.7394740097711452, \"rank\": 0.3381428730221171, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1123, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9453416793622118, \"rank\": 0.05781154524183723, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamish Mcarthur of Britain was second with 84.6 points.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9967318449787197, \"rank\": 0.0032636849160938286, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Pan Yufei was tied for 15th with Yannick Flohe of Germany.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999985893706198, \"rank\": 1.404291855580585e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999954702082328, \"rank\": 4.51752074821226e-06, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Friday's competition, the top 20 athletes in overall standings will advance to the semi-final phase.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the women's bouldering qualification, China's Luo Zhilu scored 84.8 to finish fifth among 48 climbers, behind Ievgeniia Kazbekova of Ukraine who scored 99.8 to lead the qualification.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999985893706198, \"rank\": 1.404291855580585e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luo_people\", \"score\": 0.9389553768039283, \"rank\": 0.06381094880703052, \"text\": \"Luo\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luo_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luo_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9853295483929376, \"rank\": 0.013479875891113376, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels great but the numbers are just the numbers.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's way more important that I am proud of my climbing and definitely this round is one of the best I have had,\\\" said Kazbekova.\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Luo blamed her cold for failing to conquer the first route and vowed to bring a stronger performance.\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I caught a cold and it influenced me a lot.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The routes were not very hard for me,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will try to get back to my best form as soon as possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the women's skateboarding park qualifying round, Olympic silver medalist Kokona Hiraki had a spectacular second run and took first place after scoring 83.66 points, followed by Austrian Arisa Trew (81.09) and her mate Mizuho Hasegawa (79.03).\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kokona_Hiraki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kokona Hiraki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kokona_Hiraki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kokona_Hiraki\"}, {\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9936854428467248, \"rank\": 0.0052053626961755806, \"text\": \"Austrian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 2222, \"end\": 2227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.425778926935136e-13, \"text\": \"Arisa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\"}, {\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mizuho_Financial_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.965850357580738e-19, \"text\": \"Mizuho\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mizuho_Financial_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mizuho_Financial_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 2261, \"end\": 2269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasegawa_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9977342812942308, \"rank\": 0.0022174537526994695, \"text\": \"Hasegawa\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasegawa_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasegawa_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy that I made it full in the first run already,\\\" said Hiraki.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese skateboarder Zheng Haohao failed to enter the round of last 16 after ranking 20th with 51.73.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2353, \"end\": 2360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9998580160825573, \"rank\": 0.00014167438538825028, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2374, \"end\": 2379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.999988393327895, \"rank\": 1.0849887690554226e-05, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(With input from Xinhua)  (Cover: A view of the men's skateboarding event during the Olympic Qualifier Series\\u00a0in Shanghai, China, May 16, 2024.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3782700838707245e-17, \"text\": \"Xinhua\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 2569, \"end\": 2577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.9998964091790813, \"rank\": 0.00010079563072353465, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.